OL,3,CPeople 'living shorter lives than they
OL,4,Cshould' due to austerity and cuts
OL,6,FOne of the world's leading health
OL,7,Fequity experts, Professor Sir Michael
OL,8,FMarmot, has written a damning letter
OL,9,Fto 58 MPs across England urging them
OL,10,Fto "fight for your constituents'
OL,11,Fhealth".
OL,13,FSir Michael called the findings of the
OL,14,Freport - which shows life expectancy
OL,15,Fin the North of England is lower - a
OL,16,F"dismal state of affairs".
