OL,3,CPeople 'living shorter lives than they
OL,4,Cshould' due to austerity and cuts
OL,6,FAmong the leading MPs highlighted in
OL,7,Fthe report who have "particularly
OL,8,Fconcerning health trends" in their
OL,9,Fconstituencies are former Prime
OL,10,FMinister Liz Truss, Levelling Up
OL,11,FSecretary Michael Gove and former
OL,12,FHealth Secretary Steve Barclay.
OL,14,FResearchers examined every local
OL,15,Fauthority in England to plot levels of
OL,16,Fhealth, inequalities in health, and
OL,17,Fcuts in their spending power.
