OL,3,CPeople 'living shorter lives than they
OL,4,Cshould' due to austerity and cuts
OL,6,FThey identified 17 local authorities
OL,7,Fwith statistically significant
OL,8,Fincreases in inequalities in life
OL,9,Fexpectancy between 2010-12 and the
OL,10,Fstart of the Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,12,FThe analysis - which used data from
OL,13,Fthe Office for National Statistics,
OL,14,Fthe Office for Health Improvement and
OL,15,FDisparities and the National Audit
OL,16,FOffice - highlights which local areas
OL,17,Fare "falling behind" when it comes to
OL,18,Fhealth.
