OL,6,FIn his letter to Prime Minister Rishi
OL,7,FSunak, Sir Michael, who published a
OL,8,Fseminal review into health
OL,9,Finequalities in England in 2010, said
OL,10,Fausterity and funding cuts have
OL,11,F"harmed health and worsened health
OL,12,Finequalities".
OL,14,FHe said life expectancy is "stalling"
OL,15,Fwhich he described as a "tragic waste".
