OL,6,FSir Michael has written letters to the
OL,7,FMPs whose constituencies lie wholly or
OL,8,Fpartially in these areas, including
OL,9,FCulture Secretary Lucy Frazer,
OL,10,FConservative Party Chairman Richard
OL,11,FHolden, Justice Minister Edward Argar,
OL,12,Fformer Immigration Minister Robert
OL,13,FJenrick, and former Health Minister
OL,14,FMaggie Throup.
OL,16,FHe has also written to the leaders of
OL,17,Fall major political parties demanding
OL,18,Faction.
