OL,6,FHe added: "This is a dismal state of
OL,7,Faffairs. I'm saying to party leaders:
OL,8,Fstop policies harming health and
OL,9,Fwidening health inequalities.
OL,11,F"To MPs: if you care about the health
OL,12,Fof your constituents, you must be
OL,13,Fappalled by their deteriorating
OL,14,Fhealth. It's time for action and
OL,15,Fpolitical leadership across the board.
