OL,6,F"Action is needed on the social
OL,7,Fdeterminants of health ` the
OL,8,Fconditions in which people are born,
OL,9,Fgrow, live, work and age. These social
OL,10,Fconditions are the main causes of
OL,11,Fhealth inequalities."
OL,13,F"We need you to fight for all your
OL,14,Fconstituents' health. They are
OL,15,Fsuffering avoidable ill-health and
OL,16,Fliving shorter lives than they should
OL,17,Fdue to poor policies and cuts to
OL,18,Fessential services," Sir Michael added.
