OL,7,FEngland where the difference in female
OL,8,Flife expectancy between the least
OL,9,Fdeprived and most deprived
OL,10,Fneighbourhoods showed a "significant
OL,11,Fincrease" between 2010-12 and 2017-19,
OL,12,Falong with three local authorities
OL,13,Fwhere the same occurred for males.
